---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Support — Chitti" description="Get help with Chitti — your AI beauty companion. Find answers to common questions or contact our support team.">

  <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text">Support</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-light">
        We're here to help you get the most out of Chitti.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-10">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">How does Chitti analyze my skin?</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-light">
                Chitti uses multi-angle photo capture to assess 13 skin attributes including hydration, texture, dark spots, and pore size. Your photos are processed in real-time and are never stored on our servers.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Is my data private?</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-light">
                Yes. Your photos are never permanently stored. All data is encrypted, and we use row-level security so only you can access your information. You can delete your account and all data at any time from the app settings.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">How do I delete my account?</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-light">
                Go to your Profile tab in the app, tap Settings, and select "Delete Account." This permanently removes all your data — profile, conversations, products, and preferences.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">What AI specialists are available?</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-light">
                Chitti provides dedicated AI specialists for skincare, haircare, and makeup. Each specialist knows your products, routines, and skin analysis — so advice is personalized from the very first message.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-white p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text">Is Chitti free to use?</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-light">
                Yes, Chitti is free to use. No credit card required.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Can't find what you're looking for? We'd love to hear from you.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="mt-1 flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" /></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-text">Email</p>
                <a href="mailto:support@chitti.me" class="text-sm text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 hover:decoration-primary">support@chitti.me</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border bg-bg-cream p-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">App Issues</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            If you're experiencing a bug or technical issue with the app, please email us at
            <a href="mailto:support@chitti.me" class="font-medium text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 hover:decoration-primary">support@chitti.me</a>
            with a brief description of the problem and your device model. We typically respond within 24 hours.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
